  '-p[Print point size information, including a summary of mean]' \
  '-r[Print ratio of length to area for closed contours.]' \
  '-e[Print properties of equivalent ellipses for closed contours.]' \
  '-F[Print full report on the objects, a collection of summary...]' \
  '-o[Print data only from the objects given in the list, a...]:value' \
  '-g[# Print data only from objects in the object group with the...]' \
  '-i[Analyze for inside contours and adjust computed volume by...]' \
  '-x[x]:value' \
  '-y[Compute areas and volumes within the subvolume specified by...]:value' \
  '-z[Compute areas and volumes within the subvolume specified by...]:value' \
  '-t[Truncate objects by their respective clipping planes; enter...]:value' \
  '-v[will give some summary information about each closed...]' \
  '-f[Write output to given filename instead of to standard...]:file:_files' \
  '*:file:_files' && ret=0

return ret
